data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. BACK ON THE MARKET!!! due to buyer did not secure escrow. Motivated Seller, for this well maintained 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom home in the desirable Bonnie Bay Subdivision. Located in a non-flood zone, providing peace of mind and security.This home has an oversized 2-car garage, two master bedrooms with ensuite baths, complemented by a hall bath, and a laundry room. The heart of this home is the kitchen! It has been tastefully updated to meet the standards of modern living. Noteworthy features include: newer windows, AC 2018, and an exciting opportunity for the buyer to choose the color of their new shingle roof! Which, will be installed before closing. Situated in a prime location, this gem is remarkably convenient to shopping, dining, Gulf Beaches, and just a short ride to the downtown St. Pete waterfront. It is a rare find that won't last long in today's competitive market. Don't miss out – schedule a showing now to experience the beauty, and comfort this home has to offer!
